        <Historic_Flag>Current</Historic_Flag>
        <Parent_String>luminescence [300056214], light-related concepts [300056030], energy-related concepts [300073690], energy and related concepts [300055211], physics concepts [300229371], physical sciences concepts [300065446], scientific concepts [300056006], Associated Concepts (hierarchy name) [300055126], Associated Concepts Facet [300264086]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
